  "acceptance": [
    "不同卡 disjoint、same-file disjoint、same-file ambiguous、CID overlap 都能建立各自 isolated proposal lane。",
    "R1 同卡第二 lane 仍穩定 `ATM_LOCK_CONFLICT`；合法 adopt/takeover 可接手原 lane。",
